{"tid":1090245,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《AKIRA 阿基拉》真人版傳將開拍 Leonardo DiCaprio監製","createTime":"2019-04-03T10:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T15:50:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b19c6bb009750dcd1993b0ae230e768dfe01d6e6","tid":1090245,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:31:12.000Z","msg":"根據 The Hollywood Reporter 報導，加州電影委員會於近日正式發佈得到「年度影視退稅計畫獎勵」的名單，竟意外地揭示了 Warner Bros. 眾多的新片計畫，其一就包括了《AKIRA 阿基拉》真人版電影。該片將由金獎影帝 Leonardo DiCaprio 領旗下公司 Appian Way Productions 作監製，並預計由《Thor: Ragnarok》導演 Taika Waititi 執導。<br />\n<br />\n《AKIRA 阿基拉》真人版電影確定將於加州開拍，預計投入 $9200 萬美元的預算，拍攝 71 天，\b參與團隊的成員工資將達到 $4300 萬美元，另外也確定獲得 $1850萬美元的退稅獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/4/leonardo-dicaprio-akira-california-tax-credit-allocated\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2019%2F4%2Fleonardo-dicaprio-akira-california-tax-credit-allocated&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5BF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=2381df9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2019/4/leonardo-dicaprio-akira-california-tax-credit-allocated</a>"},{"pid":"a303600bdb15577e2188a36cfbb4fcf9fc9e8f06","tid":1090245,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"點呀 又變哂鬼佬呀"},{"pid":"86e808b88d9ceb6f57ccfea2dac091aa68ed2639","tid":1090245,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"話拍AKIRA真人版就黎由中學講到大學畢業都未拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89f854901b3a063a07279d9fe9b01b9e9515ccb","tid":1090245,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86e808b88d9ceb6f57ccfea2dac091aa68ed2639","tid":1090245,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,